### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  OCR PARSER SERVICE — Full API Verification
###  Base URL routed through API Gateway: http://localhost:8080
###
###  Requires: a sample image or PDF file on your filesystem.
###  Set @sampleImage to an absolute path to a receipt/bill image.
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl     = http://localhost:8080/api
@sampleImage = /home/vergin_jose/IdeaProjects/Personal-Finance-Assistant/requests/ocr-parser/image3.png
@samplePdf   = /home/vergin_jose/IdeaProjects/Personal-Finance-Assistant/requests/ocr-parser/Receipt.pdf
@userEmail = testverify@gmail.com
@userPassword = tempPass123

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  SETUP: Login to get token and userId
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  1. PROCESS IMAGE — upload a JPG/PNG receipt
###     Expected: 200 with extracted financial data
###     (userId, name, amount, type, category, currency, description)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/bill/process/{{login.response.body.userId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="receipt.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< {{sampleImage}}
------boundary--

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  2. PROCESS PDF — upload a PDF invoice
###     Expected: 200 with extracted financial data
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/bill/process/{{login.response.body.userId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="invoice.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< {{samplePdf}}
------boundary--

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  3. VALIDATION — missing file param
###     Expected: 400 Bad Request with message about missing 'file'
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/bill/process/{{login.response.body.userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  4. VALIDATION — wrong content type (send JSON, not multipart)
###     Expected: 400 Bad Request — not image or PDF
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/bill/process/{{login.response.body.userId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="data.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{"invalid": "file"}
------boundary--

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  5. UNAUTHENTICATED — no token
###     Expected: 401 Unauthorized from API Gateway
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/bill/process/some-user-id
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="receipt.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< {{sampleImage}}
------boundary--
